headline: Snap-on Incorporated to Webcast 2025 Annual Shareholder Meeting
summary: KENOSHA, Wis., April 10, 2025--Snap-on will webcast its 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders live on Thursday, April 24 at 10:00 a.m. Central.
